
'''Network Futures'''


URL = http://www-rcf.usc.edu/%7Efbar/netfutures.html


=Description=

"These are first drafts of three possible network futures, prepared for discussion at the Networked Publics Conference (Annenberg Center for Communication, April 28-29, 2006.) They were meant to stimulate debate during the conference.


'''Scenario 1: NeutralNet'''

What could happen if congress passed a network neutrality law?


'''Scenario 2: TCNOtopia'''

What if Telcos and Cable companies were in complete control of the networks' future?


'''Scenario 3: Automata'''

What if ad-hoc, self-organizing mesh networks were all we needed to communicate?"
(http://www-rcf.usc.edu/%7Efbar/netfutures.html)


